Package ai.test.sdk

package ai.test.sdk
Contains the main classes for the Test.ai (Fluffy Dragon) SDK. These classes provide simple wrappers around existing appium functionality to seamlessly incorporate Test.ai's powerful element classification technology.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    TestAiDriver<T>
    A convenient wrapper around AppiumDriver which calls out to Test.ai to improve the accuracy of identified elements.
    TestAiElement
    An enhanced RemoteWebElement which uses the results of the Test.ai classifier for improved accuracy.
